Package src.swimmingpoolproblem.models.resources

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Resource
    The Resource interface describes a resource which can be contained in a ResourcePool and which can be provided to a ResourcefulUser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ResourcefulUser<R extends Resource>
    ResourcefulUser describes a user taking Resource from a pool.
    ResourcePool<R extends Resource>
    The ResourcePool class describes a pool containing some resources which can be taken from this pool and then freed back to the pool.
